         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="15948b80-baf5-4b44-bd26-005df1de22b2"/>
               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Each gram of diflorasone diacetate ointment contains 0.5 mg diflorasone diacetate in an ointment base.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Chemically, diflorasone diacetate is 6α, 9-difluoro-11β,17,21-trihydroxy-16β-methylpregna-1,4-diene-3,20-dione 17,21-diacetate. The structural formula is represented below:</paragraph>
                  <table width="100%" styleCode="Noautorules">
                     <col width="20%" align="left" valign="middle"/>
                     <col width="55%" align="center" valign="middle"/>
                     <col width="25%" align="left" valign="bottom"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <tr>
                           <td/>
                           <td>
                              <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM1"/>
                           </td>
                           <td>molecular formula:<br/>C<sub>26</sub>H<sub>32</sub>F<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>
                              <br/>
                              <br/>molecular weight:<br/>494.54</td>
                        </tr>
                     </tbody>
                  </table>
                  <paragraph>Each gram of diflorasone diacetate ointment contains 0.5 mg diflorasone diacetate in an ointment base of glyceryl monostearate, propylene glycol and white petrolatum.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20180817"/>
               <component>
                  <observationMedia ID="MM1">
